{"tid":1900572,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 捐兩億韓元　協助弱勢族群、醫生協會對抗疫情！","createTime":"2020-02-27T09:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T05:34:43.000Z","uid":244704,"like":71,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f4b43ff0c462b0242f503c8dfa1fddb1396f80","tid":1900572,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2020-02-27/124618-818723.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2020-02-27%2F124618-818723.png&h=608b1191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著韓國的 COVID-19 疫情轉趨嚴重，一向熱心公益的 IU 再度慷慨解囊，一舉捐出兩億分別援助不同單位！<br />\n<br />\n國際救援開發非政府組織 Good Neighbors 今天（27 日）透露 IU 最近捐出了一億韓元，希望用於優先協助大邱、慶尚北道的低收入戶和弱勢家庭，供他們購買口罩、消毒劑⋯⋯等防疫用品，以便防止並對抗 COVID-19 疫情蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2020-02-27/124618-818725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2020-02-27%2F124618-818725.jpg&h=db791008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGood Neighbors 表示：「真的非常感謝 IU 伸出溫暖的援手，協助最迫切需要幫助的低收入戶和弱勢族群孩子們，我們會與大家一起努力全力以赴，儘早克服 COVID-19 危機。」<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，IU 更另外捐了一億韓元給大韓醫生協會，為當前在第一線和病毒奮戰的醫界人員提供後援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2020-02-27/124618-818734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2020-02-27%2F124618-818734.jpg&h=00a804d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa9c801fb93385b24d137117d30df70721f3c145","tid":1900572,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/06266b8125768fe7a5a4e1e3d9299282/46885a95c01f6920-08/s250x400/8c419e7aeaea754700092ff4564a9fefbef04cbe.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F06266b8125768fe7a5a4e1e3d9299282%2F46885a95c01f6920-08%2Fs250x400%2F8c419e7aeaea754700092ff4564a9fefbef04cbe.gifv&h=ed3035df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/fc33b32e1f2c8b6f7